Define [[summarize]] taking numbers:
    {{ compute the mean, median and count of numbers into named variables mean_v median_v and count_v }}
    Do [[print]](count_v).
    Do [[print]](mean_v).
    Do [[print]](median_v).
    Give back mean_v.

Set data to <2, 3, 5, 7, 11, 13>.
Do [[summarize]](data).
